```csharp
using Pulumi;
using AwsNative = Pulumi.AwsNative;

class MyStack : Stack
{
    public MyStack()
    {
        var apsWorkspace = new AwsNative.APS.Workspace("apsWorkspace", new AwsNative.APS.WorkspaceArgs
        {
            Alias = "TestWorkspace",
            Tags = 
            {
                new AwsNative.APS.Inputs.WorkspaceTagArgs
                {
                    Key = "BusinessPurpose",
                    Value = "LoadTesting",
                },
            },
        });
    }

}
```
